name: Alien May Help!
description:
Alien may help!
Adventure game for StartupCitiesJam.

Our game is a 2D platform game in which a girl is trapped in a cave and has to collect 10 pieces for an alien, because if she helps him he will help her out of that place. The alien helps her with a double jump ability, moving objects or destroying barriers.

Made by: Crimin, Elentar, AlbertoDelarc, Pastaliyon.
